drugi dan manje...

00:07:23.522 --> 00:07:27.390
Nije mi ugodno kad
gledam samu sebe.

00:07:27.392 --> 00:07:30.493
Nemoj se zamarati s time.

00:07:30.495 --> 00:07:32.694
