00:37:44.641 --> 00:37:46.574
Napravio sam dobar posao na zidu,

00:37:46.576 --> 00:37:49.110
i bilo je dobro.

00:37:49.112 --> 00:37:53.748
I sreo sam... sestre,
i one su...

00:37:53.750 --> 00:37:56.684
Bile su... vrlo zanimljive.

00:37:56.686 --> 00:37:59.753
Zahvalne su...
Drago im je što sam ovdje, pa...

00:38:00.522 --> 00:38:03.358
