pa zato...

00:39:07.123 --> 00:39:09.657
Blagoslovili ste ga, pa je...
-Mislim,

00:39:09.659 --> 00:39:12.293
nemoj to nikome govoriti, ali...

00:39:12.295 --> 00:39:15.362
Kako bih mogao?
